Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女的血可以治疗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.33,0:02:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女的血是万灵药
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是成年魔女的血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的伤很浅的 不要紧的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 别动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘 别出声
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馆主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒过来了吗 琉妃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:03:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 这是给琉妃小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 大家都有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然想用这种东西来拉拢我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有些话想跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和我说？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于那个山丘的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.56,0:03:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个山丘很早以前就是魔女的栖息之处了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是无忧无虑 安分地生活而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便闯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行没有必要的破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以「开发」这样无聊的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肆意捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肆意破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肆意践踏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些你们人类同伴残暴的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们现在听了又能怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫 你能理解我们对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护我们自己的栖息之处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护魔女之丘 只有毁灭人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界上 一个不剩地…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 把要夺取那个山丘的家伙全都杀掉就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要杀掉的只有人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人和妖怪 生命的重量有什么差距么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀掉人类有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀掉不就好了么！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有其他方法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用起冲突就可以解决的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 到现在做什么都没有用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馆主大人要给人类以惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馆主大人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「惩罚」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为自己是个很伟大的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了自己的目的而伤害别人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 那才是「肆意」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就和人类一样了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:04:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 那个有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 那就是魔女的处事方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女好可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女不可怕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好 魔女不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个山丘被夺走了 我就没有栖息之处了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那琉妃就来阳海学园好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 离开居住已久的土地可能会有些寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校园生活也很有愉快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起学习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 干脆一起加入新闻部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香 Nice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那就有两个魔女了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛 你们两个别吵啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们的脑子冷静下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是脑子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在还来得及改变我的生存方式吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馆主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我 馆主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对 没有做背叛…馆主大人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉妃小姐不见了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉妃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉妃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉妃小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你们再踏入这里一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管…是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该有其他方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 琉妃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:07:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人的尸体下培养了植物妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙是保护馆主大人的魔女之丘的忠实的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 月音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的 月音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一个小魔女 耍什么派头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对月音出手的家伙 不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音的一根手指
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不会让你们碰到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:08:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你们全部来血祭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉妃小姐 住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算对手是妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明还听得见萌香的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但脚却不能动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香 告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我能做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为人类 我能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这么爱乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 多亏了你 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻的血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本周结果 仅仅一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉妃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保护魔女之丘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是馆主大人的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比刚才的更大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 请放了月音 琉妃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是馆主大人的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是馆主大人的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是馆主大人的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馆主大人 究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别墅？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡梦 紫 美逸 月音就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉妃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪 月音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去馆主大人那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馆主大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个别墅里 馆主大人在…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音 太危险了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你才危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩一边凉快去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音 快点去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 胡梦 小紫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还是个小鬼头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡梦才是 身手真敏捷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:12:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身上有那么重的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 第一次羡慕小鬼头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胸对手很好瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等打倒了更大的敌人后 知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那些妖怪原来是被这些根操纵的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有琉妃小姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…你就是…馆主大人…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放了琉妃小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和这些虾兵蟹将打到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打到他们全灭为止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起的话 没什么难的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是说说罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡梦 白雪 看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉妃小姐 我们明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们马上就离开这个山丘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请原谅我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在对这家伙说什么都白费
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受玷污魔女之丘的惩罚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 琉妃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有人因为琉妃小姐这么做而高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦 至少为了馆主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馆主大人什么的 不是不存在的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馆主大人就在别墅里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 那个别墅里的馆主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉妃 琉妃 琉妃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉妃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馆主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也许很愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做的事和人类一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馆主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又让你变成一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉妃 我永远和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉妃小姐 其实也是明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馆主大人已经不在这个世界上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不愿承认 不愿接受的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个琉妃小姐 不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在琉妃小姐的体内制造了一个馆主大人的虚像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 不行 琉妃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用那个禁断的魔法的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再也无法回到从前的姿态了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉妃小姐——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉妃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都毁灭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太乱来了 琉妃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无法回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都无法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉妃小姐 住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把魔具…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔具？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的魔杖拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡梦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭…这种程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别认为这么容易就赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个魔法并不只是巨大化而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我正吸收其他生物的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转化成自己的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 也包括身为吸血鬼的你的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交给我紫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔力之源玛基里尼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请倾听汝之后裔的请求 实现吾之愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 美逸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就趁现在 萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把琉妃小姐的魔具给…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们魔女 没有魔具就无法施魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也许无法变回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 萌香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让琉妃小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让琉妃小姐住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能死在这种愚蠢的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切…一切都毁灭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起破坏 更想要血
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉妃喜欢的东西是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…冰淇淋！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.41,0:20:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这个魔女 馆主大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢馆主大人了~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果 什么都没做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我更努力点的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:20:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是月音的错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 这么好吃的鱼儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 已经到回去的时间了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这个诡异的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长可是从补习的地狱里奇迹生还啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更高兴地…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉…琉妃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 你们认识她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似要说welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才在海里发现这孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被什么东西保护一样浮在水面上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.54,0:21:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被什么…所保护一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 走错路了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快回…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方 还有如此美丽的山丘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.41,0:22:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是 魔女代代珍惜的向日葵园地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也会珍惜它的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.19,0:22:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远永远地珍惜它
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回别墅去吧 我们的家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.44,0:22:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.34,0:24:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假结束了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感动的牌最后都糟蹋了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.85,0:24:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆让你永远都放暑假好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.06,0:24:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.35,0:24:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 新学期与吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.41,0:24:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你抱在怀里 亲~
